{"tid":1193352,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"曼聯有意用50萬磅周薪租巴利一年,同支付一筆租借費","createTime":"2019-06-09T00:51:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-09T07:20:53.000Z","uid":173952,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"11459530036f34c757119a87da4aeb8ed5adb39f","tid":1193352,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T00:51:47.000Z","msg":"《週日鏡報》消息，儘管曼聯和熱刺都對貝爾有意，但他們無意支付皇馬的要價7500萬鎊。<br />\n不過，曼聯將再次嘗試拿下貝爾，他們提出的方案是租借1年，然後再有延長1年的選項，這樣一來皇馬也要能省下5000萬鎊的薪金。此外，曼聯還願意支付一筆租借費。<br />\n目前貝爾的態度堅定，還不知道他是否會願意去曼聯效力，畢竟下賽季曼聯也沒有歐冠可踢。<br />\n報導稱，曼聯方面希望能簽下一名大牌來讓球迷們興奮，貝爾若加盟，他的薪金將和桑切斯差不多。"},{"pid":"b779717d62e929349acf25a268c98113252d7bb7","tid":1193352,"uid":191926,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T00:53:41.000Z","msg":"貝爾若加盟，他的薪金將和桑切斯差不多<br />\n<br />\n咁多人免費踢波<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ffc53ae9a0819ebfa71c537fa299d75c1f51857","tid":1193352,"uid":233522,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T00:53:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">鏡報</span></span>"},{"pid":"00b7736654e5bb168e607d3cbe9b8b15341c36d6","tid":1193352,"uid":133130,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T00:55:22.000Z","msg":"左山右bale<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1deb4d389580a86ff261cc0aefa8a5216287b3f0","tid":1193352,"uid":43061,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T01:28:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />BALE識咩樂器可以同山神合奏?"},{"pid":"30e81de9ebc28b078caff6df4ba580eb91c8060b","tid":1193352,"uid":160555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00b7736654e5bb168e607d3cbe9b8b15341c36d6","tid":1193352,"uid":133130,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T00:55:22.000Z","msg":"左山右bale<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09